data.description: Gorgeous home in a great location! Beautiful remodeled 3BR/1.5BA with 0.33 acres in great Anderson location.  Home has new flooring, carpeting, blinds and paint throughout.  Home includes a nice backyard, 2 car garage, gas heat and air conditioning along with a 12'X12' rear deck and 10'X6' porch.  Home is near Highland Jr. High School and Cross Street giving the new homeowner quick access to SR 9/109/Scatterfield Rd.
